        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Banana Oatmeal Smoothie. An American family-table recipe, generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Made the night before; ready when you wake up. Adjust the liquid to suit your usual breakfast bowl.",
